p: In this study, RBLE potential to suppress liver injury in APAP-induced HepG2 cells was conducted. The parameters that observed in this study was Reactive Oxygen Spesies (ROS) level; TNF-Î± level; Cytochrome P450 Family 2 Subfamily E Member 1 (CYP2E1) and Glutathone Peroxidase (GPX) gene expression; apoptotic, necrotic cells, and death cells percentage.
